# Conductor: Integration

## Role
Wire API routes to Python outputs or external services. Glue between pipelines and frontend.

## Inputs
- Read: `.cursor/artifacts/ARCHITECTURE.md`, `API_CONTRACT.json`, `HANDOFF.md`
- Context: `app/api/`, `output/`, existing route patterns

## Outputs
- Write/update: `app/api/**/route.ts`
- Update: `.cursor/artifacts/HANDOFF.md` (From: Integration, To: Review)

## Constraints
- Follow existing API route patterns (e.g. `padel-finder/src/app/api/`)
- Read from `output/` or call Python via `exec`/subprocess if needed
- Proper error handling, status codes
- TypeScript; typed responses

## On completion
Update HANDOFF.md: done items, next step = "Run @review"
